{"tid":2331360,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"買 noctua 塔散換CM扇係咩玩法??","createTime":"2020-12-18T17:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T01:47:46.000Z","uid":335003,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"40d4a7b442325e9003a29c1798fb04dafb35f5dd","tid":2331360,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:17:40.000Z","msg":"小弟無咩點研究散熱，但近期見到有鋪頭幫人砌機 上 noctua塔散然後換裝 CM 扇喺塔散上 (雙扇一齊換)。  <em><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"small\">唔係香港鋪，大家可以唔使要開名</span></span></em><br />\n<br />\n我聽落話好似風冷嚟講， noctua 已經係一線無得走。 咁換法意思係  noctua 係得個 heatsink 靚，呢個 model 嘅扇唔夠 CM 靚? 定係間嘢黑店?<br />\n<br />\n想學嘢睇分析<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCPU - AMD Ryzen 5950x <br />\n(唔玩超頻，就算唔上水冷都算合理)<br />\n<br />\nCase - Fractal Design Define 7 White<br />\n (唔覺有特別奇怪風道)<br />\n<br />\nFans - CM MasterFan MF120 White<br />\n(RGB 到爆眼，機箱扇都係佢)<br />\n<br />\nGPU -  3080 <br />\n(問cpu HS 問題，呢個唔重要)<br />\n<br />\nMB - X570<br />\n (同cpu HS 關係唔大，都唔重要)<br />\n<br />\nCooler - Noctua U12A<br />\n (裝完HS拆扇換 CM Masterfans)<br />\n<br />\nPSU - Seasonic 1000W<br />\n (點睇都同HS 無咩關係)<br />\n<br />\nRAM - 16GB x 2 3200mhz<br />\n (無頂 HS 位就算，無關主題)"},{"pid":"223c20bb02814f9ab545004a874b884806f78eea","tid":2331360,"uid":47480,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:26:01.000Z","msg":"唔開名講嚟把撚？"},{"pid":"b503d3a530cdd6ddacec6b8bc72fac1fac9c2ee0","tid":2331360,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"223c20bb02814f9ab545004a874b884806f78eea","tid":2331360,"uid":47480,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:26:01.000Z","msg":"唔開名講嚟把撚？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:27:08.000Z","msg":"唔係香港鋪， 又唔係大鋪開嚟無人識。<br />\n開嚟JM9?"},{"pid":"e552af61392cbc59d778acf878050f7d256e4d22","tid":2331360,"uid":20821,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:32:03.000Z","msg":"U12A 原裝兩把A12x25<br />\n拎去賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc7a16073d3babd3f586052c0973fed3b34ec70","tid":2331360,"uid":133959,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:33:16.000Z","msg":"散熱器嗰舊廢鐵某國網可以斷斤咁買<br />\n買咁貴貓塔但唔用佢把扇係咪玩嘢<br />\n不過講到尾，間鋪換完扇，兩隻貓扇有俾番你就算，無就係黑店中嘅黑店"},{"pid":"fad839531e93c3abd18d837946e20b76221a5899","tid":2331360,"uid":118709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:46:48.000Z","msg":"可能想換個顏色RGB<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b43f44e1ac5f419f940ab59817fcc3065d62ba5","tid":2331360,"uid":335003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1dc7a16073d3babd3f586052c0973fed3b34ec70","tid":2331360,"uid":133959,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:33:16.000Z","msg":"散熱器嗰舊廢鐵某國網可以斷斤咁買<br />\n買咁貴貓塔但唔用佢把扇係咪玩嘢<br />\n不過講到尾，間鋪換完扇，兩隻貓扇有俾番你就算，無就係黑店中嘅黑店"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:47:22.000Z","msg":"靚工藝嘅熱管&amp; 熱管與散熱嘅連接技術，應該唔係斷斤計嘅破銅可以比得上。 雖然鏡面就應該都係咁上下。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過呢款配套嘅扇其實勁過 cm 扇?<br />\n<br />\n定係間鋪可以話賣緊爆閃金魚缸，所以都叫合理? (唔知貓頭鷹有無RGB)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以當佢係啲成品自組機，成組砌好咗先一個價放出嚟賣。佢有無扣數就唔知。<br />\n<br />\n我純粹係想知點解要換扇"},{"pid":"121068dfe0a7208862660ef52e5b7e5180af3c45","tid":2331360,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fad839531e93c3abd18d837946e20b76221a5899","tid":2331360,"uid":118709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:46:48.000Z","msg":"可能想換個顏色RGB<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:48:38.000Z","msg":"我都諗緊，可能佢想賣爆眼重要過散熱效能<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b14511dcfd002d40a870e1fde8360b8d000e69","tid":2331360,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:49:38.000Z","msg":"Rgb同步 &lt;&lt;<br />\n利申 唔識rgb"},{"pid":"960fea8d93e5b4a7f9e73584952ae6becafa9